# readbro

Single MCP for file reads. **Never use built-in Read.**

| Tool | When |
|------|------|
| `read_file` / `read_files` | All file reads — **layer L1 default** (not L3) |
| `pack_context` | Multi-file bug/trace — `budget: 4000`, optional `target` |
| `blast_radius` | Before editing non-trivial source |
| `session_status` | Repo health snapshot (totals, efficiency) |
| `session_gain` | Where savings come from (top files, globs) |
| `session_clear` | Clear repo cache |

**L3 = full raw** — avoid for exploration; auto-capped. Use `max_lines: -1` only when you truly need full raw.

Full guide: `~/.agents/skills/readbro/SKILL.md`
